Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和他三年沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說布蘭登·西特？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就是那個哈利·麥克道韋爾的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個危險的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙指揮的Truegrave實力之強大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至凌駕於貝爾·沃肯的Overkills之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默 直率 手腕也了得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy沒理由不器重他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來遲了啊 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Millennion的布蘭登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慈心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意把大家召集到一起 不是為了別的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位擁有的所有東部地區酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能轉讓給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 也包括酒店中貴重物品的持有權
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算開價多少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百萬尤爾如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本談不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有談判破裂的準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃 報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情報顯示東部地區40%的酒店出現了赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不採取措施就會變得不可收拾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 到去年為止都還好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了今年 生意突然變淡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你們暗中搞鬼嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 這只是提案而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓諸位的生活能安定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Millennion的資金和組織力來幫助你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全都幹掉不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人的話就撈不到什麼油水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活著利用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真不愧為哈利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些傢伙這麼容易就說OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布蘭登 現在他是Millennion力量的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是深入人心的組織形象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以工作就變得簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事件打擊了八成以上的反抗組織勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這段時間感覺上有些過分強人所難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據鮑勃的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭迪的手下一直在你周圍盯梢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼都必須遵循世間興亡交替的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候又怎麼能渾渾噩噩地放過機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時聽候吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主外的是布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主內的就是李 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利 差不多到時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 再遲到的話又會看到雪莉嘟著一張嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有打算以貝爾·沃肯為敵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 我可是愛著她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由心底的這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利是很優秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去慰勞這些組員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多一個晚上是花不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留給斯賓塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍械要保管好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想跟你好好介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的吧 雪莉·沃肯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話想一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 布蘭登自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有跟什麼人交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呀 有的吧 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒公開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 果然有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話才奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月瑪麗亞的生日宴會為什麼不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最近很喜歡的布蘭登送的裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從執事那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見一見她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很在意你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以組織老闆的身份下的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣想的話 就會像我這樣一直單身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好像有一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你步我後塵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣想的 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了布蘭登大哥 為了Truegrave
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 文治大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次能替我向布蘭登大哥道謝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月老媽住院的治療費
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知道的時候就全部由布蘭登大哥支付了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒對別人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事自己去說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說是替我這種人出的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我的話就行 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛…大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登大哥幹嘛要當黑社會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊喝酒的那幫傢伙的話就可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要錢 想出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要女人 想鬧事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還有其他的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論怎樣都可以想得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有布蘭登大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別但絕對是有和我一樣的道義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文治大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本部聯絡說有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 哈利 真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次做更開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到早上為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不能和哈利交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾是真正的黑社會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能危害到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不也是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不正是真真正正的黑社會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想變成媽媽那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你變成你媽媽那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我是黑社會的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就有了心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了哈利的話 也可以去死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像爸爸為了Big Daddy可以去死那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這固執的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是爸爸的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父女倆也要相爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相爭的話我也會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戀愛會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對代理人的女兒誘拐未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一點小事都幹不成的小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要費我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登大哥幹嘛要當黑社會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老了不中用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你這樣的小混混打傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我 別殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 別殺我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像樣啊 九頭文治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一個人行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答我 文治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是瑣碎的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想勞駕你來幹這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 文治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登 告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有這種事 所以要盡量避免擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擔心你的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有自尊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九頭文治是個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些事 坐下來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的老朋友最近不經常來這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 布蘭登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 他和他的朋友經營的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近取得了優良的業績
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登和哈利？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那兩個人很有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不認識他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我這麼考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他倆加入我的集團
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後讓他們繼承我的事業 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 得先跟他們說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的就是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞 我想聽聽你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓布蘭登…繼承組織吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織？你在…說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這麼費心真是很感激了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔做的事 傑斯塔叔叔做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 現在布蘭登和哈利在幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到的時候是四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認 我調查了叔叔你們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我對你隱瞞真相是為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑斯塔叔叔他想要讓我清清白白地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 叔叔您也想要正常地養育我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑斯塔叔叔死了 我住進了這所別墅裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後過了半年時間 布蘭登來看我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高興極了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那時候 他已經加入組織了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他加入組織是因為朋友哈利還有你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要守護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以為了追求守護你們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是偏離了正道也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就那樣加入了我的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…布蘭登他是不會動搖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己決定的事是會一直固執地堅持下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三年來一直沒有來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也有這樣做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得偏離了正道的自己沒法帶給你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻又比任何人都想要讓你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你想到了傷心的事 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是願意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算是使用權力也要把他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他還希望我能幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了他也會變得幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這算是對他的感情的回報的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織的內部出現叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他的工作就交給Truegrave了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時岡博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起以前跟你見面的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 繼續進行NECROLIZE的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究資金和材料都準備得很充分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也保證你的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NECROLIZE的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是罪孽 是惡魔一樣的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道是這樣 為什麼博士你還繼續研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算說是受到了"閃電"的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是博士還有道德和正義感的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能進行這樣的研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己選擇的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行瘋狂的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法抵抗科學的魅力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確應該封印NECROLIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你就抱著你的心中僅有的一點點正義感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碌碌無為就終此一生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要這麼選擇麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經發展至此的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會進化的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要遠遠地默默地看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要作為一個瘋狂科學家名留青史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問都不用問 你已經選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把NECROLIZE怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做什麼 也不想要運用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了對抗"閃電"那樣的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們Millennion有必要增強實力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了減少不必要的火拚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…NECROLIZE？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是第二版
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維護的時候須要把體內的血液進行替換
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外 幾乎能夠半永久性地活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經做到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你都只能墮入地獄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墮入地獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向上升
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到的地方不是地獄而是自由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼都可以任意奪取任意給與
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的自由在等著我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這種力量告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能看到更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在追求安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在盼望幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不能滿足她的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果追求的東西在遙遠彼岸的話
